SymbolTable.name: SymbolTable
SymbolTable.description: A complex type that represents all user-defined tokens in the Body of an ApexClass, ApexClassMember, or ApexTriggerMember and their associated line and column locations within the Body.

constructors.description: Constructor includes the following fields: annotations location modifiers name references visibility (available only in API versions 33.0 and earlier; scope: Global, Public, or Private) parameters

externalReferences.description: ExternalReference includes the following fields: methods name namespace references variables

methods.description: Method includes the following fields: annotations location modifiers name references visibility (available only in API versions 33.0 and earlier; scope: Global, Public, or Private) parameters returnType

properties.description: VisibilitySymbol includes the following fields: annotations location modifiers name references visibility (available only in API versions 33.0 and earlier; scope: Global, Public, or Private)

tableDeclaration.description: Symbol includes the following fields: annotations location modifiers name references

variables.description: Symbol includes the following fields: annotations location modifiers name references
